						<summary>

						<p>Pillar of the <hi rend="italic">maṇḍapa</hi> in the compound of the Rāmasvāmi temple.</p>						

						<p>This is dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1766, Krōdhi, Phālguṇa śu. 15</hi> corresponding to <hi rend="bold">1844 A.D., March 4, Monday.</hi></p>						

						<p>Records the construction of the temple of Śrī Rāma with its <hi rend="italic">Kalyāṇamaṇḍapa</hi> by Tirumalakoṇḍu, son of Gaṟṟe Koṇḍaḍu.</p>						

						</summary>
