<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī vijayābhyu 
<lb n="2" break="no"/>daya śālivāhana śa 
<lb n="3" break="no"/>kavarṣaṁbulu 1766 A 
<lb n="4" break="no"/>gunēṭi krōdhināma saṁ 
<lb n="5" break="no"/>(ṁ)vyatsara phālguṇa śu 
<lb n="6" break="no"/>ddha 15 lu śrīrāmula ka 
<lb n="7" break="no"/>ḷyāṇamaṁṭapaṁ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> garre koṁ 
<lb n="8" break="no"/>ḍani kumāruṁḍu tirumala koṁ 
<lb n="9" break="no"/>ḍu<unclear>dē</unclear>vaḷaṁ yī maṁṭapaṁ 
</p>

<p>The rest of the inscription is lost.</p>

